responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "84548E4A420C6BD4F73D38B58AF9CDAB", "Tradeskills! Sword and shield will allow you to march from here to there, but what keeps the blade sharp, what places food in ones belly, what fells the trees and erects the walls? Artisans!
